Dear Messrs. Brown and Barr: This letter responds to the Comments of PPG Industries, Inc. [``PPG''] on Proposed Final
Judgment, Stipulation and Competitive Impact Statement 

(``Comments'') submitted to the Antitrust Division over your names on August 13, 1994. The Comments include a ``Preliminary
