Dear Mr. Grimstad: This letter responds to your letter of August 10, 1994, commenting on and proposing changes in the
proposed Final Judgment (``Judgment'') in the above-captioned matter. You complained that (i) the Judgment rests
on several ``flawed assumptions'' listed in your letter that you said ``have led to a flawed result''; (ii) contrary
